lochs (0.3.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Dashboard: bearer token authentication and login modal
  * Dashboard: TLS support via socat proxy (--ssl-cert/--ssl-key)
  * Dashboard: network and volume CRUD from web UI
  * Dashboard: Lochfile editor and build page
  * Dashboard: resource history charts (CPU/memory/PIDs)
  * CLI: lochs cp — copy files between host and container
  * CLI: lochs export/import — tar-based container snapshots
  * CLI: lochs push — push images to OCI registries
  * BSDulator: /dev device emulation (/dev/null, /dev/random, etc.)
  * BSDulator: kqueue/kevent stub framework
  * BSDulator: improved signal handling (sigaction, sigprocmask)
  * Infrastructure: systemd service file
  * Infrastructure: REST API documentation (docs/api.md)

 -- Zachary Kleckner <zach@lochs.dev>  Mon, 03 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
